node.text:
📍Ba Be Lake, Vietnam

Ba Be Lake was formed over 200 million years ago, and is Vietnam's largest and highest natural lake!

🎥: @florisgone

#Vietnam #lake #travel #landscape
Ba Be Lake is Vietnam’s largest natural lake and a biodiversity hotspot, home to over 550 plant species and rare wildlife!
